reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this product because I ran out of space on my IPhone, and could no longer take any more photos. This was a problem that needed to be fixed and the other alternative would’ve been paying for more storage monthly, and I decided that I did not want to spend money every month just to keep my photos on my phone, and that I would prefer to keep my photos on a flash drive anyways to keep my photos in a safe place where I could access them any time. This product was a solution to my problem, and it was so simple to use! All you have to do is download an app on your phone to transfer the photos to the flash drive and you just insert the flash drive right into your phone. It was very easy and now I can transfer photos whenever I want and if I ever want to look back on the photos I downloaded all I have to do is insert it back in my phone or use the opposite side of the flash drive and insert it into a USB plug, like on a computer. I definitely would recommend this for everyone even if you don’t need to free up the space, because it is so nice to have your photos in a safe place!
